# DXT Manifest Version Rule

- When you change the `server` field (any nested value) or modify the `tools` list (add/remove/reorder/update any tool), bump the `version` in `dxt/manifest.json`. Do not change `dxt_version`.
- Use semantic versioning for `version` (MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH). Prefer PATCH for routine tweaks, MINOR for new tools or new server capabilities, MAJOR for breaking changes.
